{
  "doc_id": "36673",
  "text": "Core OS was prepared as described [CITATION_1] . The PhoP-His and PmrG-His proteins were purified using the Ni-NTA Spin kit (Qiagen) as described by the manufacturer. Production of free phosphate was assayed as described [CITATION_2] . Purified protein (1 mg) was incubated with core OS substrate for 30 min at 37°C. Free Pi generated in the assay was measured by malachite green assay using BIOMOL GREEN™ reagent (BIOMOL Res Laboratories) and a microplate reader at 620 nm. Data were corrected for background activity by subtracting the absorbance of the samples lacking core OS from those incubated in the presence of core OS.",
